## ⚙️ Requirements
Install required Python libraries:
```bash
pip install PyMuPDF Pillow
python main.py
[
  {
    "page": 1,
    "question": "What comes next?",
    "images": "images/page1_image1.png",
    "option_images": [
      "images/page1_image2.png",
      "images/page1_image3.png"
    ]
  }
]
